"{\"uid\": \"newsus.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-12-Los-Angeles-gears-up-for-the-2028-Summer-Olympics-1vZOm7iZcNq-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Ediz Tiyansan  Copied  The Los Angeles Coliseum has already hosted two Summer Olympic Games in 1932 and 1984. Now preparations are underway to host again in 2028.  Our correspondent Ediz Tiyansan has spoken to officials at the Los Angeles Coliseum and logistical experts about the preparations and challenges.  For more, check out our exclusive content onCGTN Nowand subscribe to our weekly newsletter,The China Report.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"